reviewText: I really like this Pioneer woman doctor and all the characters making up the town of Colorado Springs.  Each show was done so well and usually addressing a life issue found anywhere.  Of course by this Season 5, Dr Quinn was accepted as the town doctor, but some other prejudices or young people's growing pains, etc...  Would remind you a lot of Little House on the Prairie TV Show and just as family oriented.  Recommend Amazon as easy shopping and ships quickly and safely.
